             was indicted for <rs id="t18100411-108-off615" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18100411-108-off615" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18100411-108-off615" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18100411-108-cd616" type="crimeDate">24th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18100411-108-off615 t18100411-108-cd616"></join>, 14 lb. wt. of hay, value 9 d. and one peck of chaff, value 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18100411-108-victim941" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Shirley
                  <interp inst="t18100411-108-victim941" type="surname" value="Shirley"></interp>
