                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18100411-108-defend939 t18100411-108-punish620"></join>
               Fined 1 s.
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
